#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "आमुख"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwrite; is more than a text editor by &kde;. It is meant to be a "
"programmer's editor, and could be considered as at least a partial "
"alternative to more powerful editors. It may be best used in conjunction "
"with &konqueror; or &dolphin; for source file browsing for different "
"languages. &kwrite; also works very well as a simple text editor. One of "
"&kwrite;'s main features is the colorized syntax, customized for many "
"different programming languages such as: C/C++, &Java;, Python, Perl, Bash, "
"Modula 2, &HTML;, and Ada. &kwrite; has a single document interface "
"(<acronym>SDI</acronym>) allowing you to edit one file at the time per "
"window."
msgstr ""
"&kwrite; &kde; द्वारा पाठसम्पादकात् अधिकम् अस्ति। इदं प्रोग्रामरस्य सम्पादकं भवितुम् "
"अभिप्रेतम्, अधिकशक्तिशालिनः सम्पादकानां न्यूनातिन्यूनं आंशिकविकल्पः इति गणयितुं शक्यते स्म । "
"&konqueror; अथवा &dolphin; विभिन्नभाषाणां कृते स्रोतसञ्चिकाब्राउजिंग् कृते । &kwrite; "
"सरलपाठसम्पादकरूपेण अपि अतीव सुन्दरं कार्यं करोति । &kwrite;इत्यस्य मुख्यविशेषतासु एकं "
"वर्णयुक्तं वाक्यविन्यासः अस्ति, यत् अनेकविभिन्नप्रोग्रामिंगभाषाणां कृते अनुकूलितं भवति यथा: C/C+"
"+, &Java;, Python, Perl, Bash, Modula 2, &HTML;, Ada च &kwrite; एकं दस्तावेज-"
"अन्तरफलकं (<acronym>SDI</acronym>) अस्ति यत् प्रति-विण्डो-समये एकां सञ्चिकां सम्पादयितुं "
"शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwrite; is a simple interface to the &katepart; component also used by "
"&kate;, &kdevelop;, and other applications from &kde; that require advanced "
"text editing. Therefore, complete documentation for all the features of "
"&kwrite; can be found in the <ulink url=\"help:/katepart\">&katepart; "
"Handbook</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&kwrite; &katepart; घटकः &kate;, &kdevelop;, इत्यादिभिः अनुप्रयोगैः अपि उपयुज्यते "
"&kde; येषु उन्नतपाठसम्पादनस्य आवश्यकता भवति। अतः &kwrite; <ulink url=\"help:/"
"katepart\">&katepart; हस्तपुस्तिका</ulink>।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Line Options"
msgstr "आदेशपङ्क्तिविकल्पाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Though &kwrite; may most often be started from the &plasma; application "
"starter, or a desktop icon, it can also be opened at the command line prompt "
"of a terminal window. There are a few useful options that are available when "
"doing this."
msgstr ""
"यद्यपि &kwrite; प्रायः &plasma; application starter, अथवा desktop icon, इदं "
"terminal window इत्यस्य command line prompt इत्यत्र अपि उद्घाटयितुं शक्यते । एतत् कुर्वन् "
"कतिपये उपयोगिनो विकल्पाः उपलभ्यन्ते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many other applications that use &katepart; offer similar command line "
"options."
msgstr ""
"अन्ये बहवः अनुप्रयोगाः ये &katepart; समानानि आदेशपङ्क्तिविकल्पानि प्रदातुं शक्नुवन्ति।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify a File"
msgstr "एकं सञ्चिकां निर्दिशन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By specifying the path and name of a particular file the user can have "
"&kwrite; open (or create) that file immediately upon startup. This option "
"might look something like the following:"
msgstr ""
"सञ्चिकाविशेषस्य मार्गं नाम च निर्दिश्य उपयोक्तुः &kwrite; प्रारम्भे तत्क्षणमेव तां सञ्चिकां "
"उद्घाटयन्तु (अथवा रचयन्तु) । एषः विकल्पः निम्नलिखितवत् किमपि दृश्यते ।"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:88
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>kwrite</command>\n"
#| "<option><replaceable>/home/myhome/docs/myfile.txt</replaceable></option>\n"
#| "</userinput>"
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>kwrite</command> "
"<option><replaceable>/home/myhome/docs/myfile.txt</replaceable></option>\n"
"</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>% .</prompt><userinput><command> क्व्रिते</"
"command><option><replaceable> / गृह / myhome / docs / myfile.txt</"
"replaceable></option></userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "Specify a file on the Internet"
msgstr "अन्तर्जालस्य सञ्चिकां निर्दिशन्तु"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The above-mentioned method could even be used to open files on the Internet "
"(if the user has an active connection at the time.) An example of this might "
"look like the following:"
msgstr ""
"उपरि उल्लिखिता पद्धतिः अन्तर्जालस्य सञ्चिकाः उद्घाटयितुं अपि उपयोक्तुं शक्यते स्म (यदि "
"तस्मिन् समये उपयोक्तुः सक्रियः संयोजनः अस्ति ।) अस्य उदाहरणं निम्नलिखितम् इव दृश्यते ।"

#. Tag: screen
#: index.docbook:98
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>kwrite</command>\n"
#| "<option><replaceable>ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde/README</replaceable>\n"
#| "</option></userinput>"
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>kwrite</command> "
"<option><replaceable>ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde/README</replaceable>\n"
"</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>% .</prompt><userinput><command> क्व्रिते</"
"command><option><replaceable> ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde/README इति ग्रन्थः</"
"replaceable></option></userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Command Line Options"
msgstr "अन्ये आदेशपङ्क्तिविकल्पाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following command line help options are available"
msgstr "निम्नलिखित आदेशपङ्क्तिसहाय्यविकल्पाः उपलभ्यन्ते"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kwrite</command> <option>--help</option>"
msgstr "<command>क्व्रिते</command><option value=--help> --साहाय्यम्‌</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "This lists the most basic options available at the command line."
msgstr "एतेन आदेशपङ्क्तौ उपलब्धाः मूलभूतविकल्पाः सूचीबद्धाः सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kwrite</command> <option>--author</option>"
msgstr "<command>क्व्रिते</command><option value=--author> --लेखकः</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists &kwrite;'s authors in the terminal window."
msgstr "टर्मिनल् विण्डो मध्ये &kwrite; इत्यस्य लेखकान् सूचीबद्धं करोति ।"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kwrite</command> <option>-v</option>, <option>--version</option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>क्व्रिते</command><option value=-v> -वि</option> , ९.<option value=--"
"version> --संस्करण</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists version information for the application."
msgstr "अनुप्रयोगस्य कृते संस्करणसूचनाः सूचीबद्धं करोति ।"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kwrite</command> <option>--license</option>"
msgstr "<command>क्व्रिते</command><option value=--license> --अनुज्ञापत्रम्</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shows license information."
msgstr "अनुज्ञापत्रसूचना दर्शयति।"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kwrite</command> <option>--desktopfile</option> "
"<parameter>filename</parameter>"
msgstr ""
"<command>क्व्रिते</command><option value=--desktopfile> --डेस्कटॉपसञ्चिका</"
"option><parameter> सञ्चिकानाम</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "The base file name of the desktop entry for this application."
msgstr "अस्य अनुप्रयोगस्य कृते डेस्कटॉप् प्रविष्टेः आधारसञ्चिकानाम ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is in particular useful for wrapper applications and applications "
"having in general multiple desktop files. Thus each desktop file can have "
"its own command line for the <option>Exec</option> entry."
msgstr ""
"एतत् विशेषतया रैपर-अनुप्रयोगानाम्, सामान्यतया बहु-डेस्कटॉप्-सञ्चिकानां च अनुप्रयोगानाम् कृते "
"उपयोगी भवति । एवं प्रत्येकं डेस्कटॉप् सञ्चिकायाः कृते स्वकीया आदेशपङ्क्तिः भवितुम् "
"अर्हति<option value=Exec> Exec</option> प्रवेशः ।"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kwrite</command> <option>-e</option>, <option>--encoding</option> "
"<parameter>encoding</parameter>"
msgstr ""
"<command>क्व्रिते</command><option value=-e> -ङ</option> , ९.<option value=--"
"encoding> --एन्कोडिंग्</option><parameter> एन्कोडिंग्</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Causes &kwrite; to use the specified encoding for the document."
msgstr "कारणानि &kwrite; दस्तावेजस्य कृते निर्दिष्टं एन्कोडिंग् उपयोक्तुं ।"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kwrite</command> <option>-l</option>, <option>--line</option> "
"<parameter>line</parameter>"
msgstr ""
"<command>क्व्रिते</command><option value=-l> -l</option> , ९.<option value=--"
"line> --पंक्ति</option><parameter> पंक्ति</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigate to the specified line after opening the document."
msgstr "दस्तावेजं उद्घाट्य निर्दिष्टपङ्क्तौ गच्छन्तु ।"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kwrite</command> <option>-c</option>, <option>--column</option> "
"<parameter>column</parameter>"
msgstr ""
"<command>क्व्रिते</command><option value=-c> -ग</option> , ९.<option value=--"
"column> --स्तम्भ</option><parameter> स्तम्भ:</parameter>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigate to the specified column after opening the document."
msgstr "दस्तावेजं उद्घाट्य निर्दिष्टस्तम्भे गच्छन्तु ।"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>kwrite</command> <option>-i</option>, <option>--stdin</option>"
msgstr ""
"<command>क्व्रिते</command><option value=-i> -अहम्‌</option> , ९.<option value=--"
"stdin> --stdin</option>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Causes &kwrite; to read the document content from STDIN. This is similar to "
"the common option <option>-</option> used in many command line programs, and "
"allows you to pipe command output into &kwrite;."
msgstr ""
"कारणानि &amp;kwrite; STDIN तः दस्तावेजसामग्री पठितुं । एतत् सामान्यविकल्पसदृशम् "
"अस्ति<option value=-> - ९.</option> अनेकेषु आदेशपङ्क्तिकार्यक्रमेषु उपयुज्यते, तथा च &amp;"
"kwrite;मध्ये आदेशनिर्गमं पाइप् कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

